  "200 fish per year": "",
  "100 fish per year": "",
  "P'(t) = [5000(t+10) - 5000t]/(t+10)^2 = 50000/(t+10)^2. At t = 15: P'(15) = 50000/625 = 80 fish per year.": "",
  "A car's fuel efficiency in mpg is modeled by E(v) = v * (60 - 0.5v)/(v + 10) where v is speed in mph. Using the quotient rule, what is E'(30)?": "",
  "-0.15625 mpg per mph": "",
